1. Nadam se da ću *preživeti* ovu nedelju punu sastanaka. (I hope I will survive this week full of meetings.)
2. Kako si *preživeo* prošlogodišnje leto? (How did you survive last year's summer?)
3. Oni su *preživeli* brodolom i bili spašeni posle pet dana na moru. (They survived a shipwreck and were rescued after five days at sea.)
4. Neki ljudi se mogu *preživeti* samo od ljubavi. (Some people can survive solely on love.)
5. *Preživeo* sam mnogo toga u životu, ali ovaj izazov je bio najteži do sada. (I have survived a lot in life, but this challenge was the toughest so far.)
6. Njihova firma je uspela da *preživi* ekonomsku krizu zahvaljujući mudrim poslovnim odlukama. (Their company managed to survive the economic crisis thanks to wise business decisions.)
7. Pokušavam da *preživim* na ovom poslu dok ne nađem nešto bolje. (I'm trying to survive this job until I find something better.)
8. Ona je uspela *preživeti* tešku bolest zahvaljujući snazi svog uma i volji za životom. (She managed to survive a serious illness thanks to the strength of her mind and will to live.)